queries.sql: SELECT count(distinct influencer_id), network, sum(post_total)as post_total, date(create_date)as date, WEEK(create_date)AS week, dayname(create_date)as day, min(time(create_date)), max(time(create_date)) FROM influencer_stat_post_recent WHERE WEEK(create_date) = '1' and year(create_date) = '2023' GROUP BY DATE,network,week

SELECT network, month(create_date)AS month, year(create_date)AS YEAR, DATE_FORMAT(create_date,'%Y-%m') year_month_, MONTHNAME(create_date)AS name_month, COUNT(DISTINCT influencer_id) influencer, sum(post_total)total_post FROM influencer_stat_post_recent WHERE year(create_date) = '2022' GROUP BY month,network
